article.headline: Lewis, Pascarelli score 14 as Marist knocks off New Hampshire 54-49
article.description: — Elijah Lewis and Josh Pascarelli both scored 14 points as Marist beat New Hampshire 54-49 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Lewis, Pascarelli score 14 as Marist knocks off New Hampshire 54-49
article.story: POUGHKEEPSIE, N.Y. -- — Elijah Lewis and Josh Pascarelli both scored 14 points as Marist beat New Hampshire 54-49 on Saturday. Lewis added six rebounds for the Red Foxes (4-1). Pascarelli shot 5 of 11 (2 for 4 from 3-point range). Jaden Daughtry finished 4 of 5 from the field to finish with nine points. The Wildcats (2-7) were led in scoring by Davide Poser, who finished with 11 points. Khalil Badru added 10 points and six rebounds for New Hampshire. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
